gamespot.com/articles/mario-kart-lego-sets-are-available-now-check-out-all-six-in-the-launch-lineup/1100-6528603/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6528603\"\u003eMario Kart\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/legos-animal-crossing-series-expands-with-three-new-sets/1100-6528502/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6528502\"\u003eAnimal Crossing\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/six-new-star-wars-lego-sets-available-now-including-baby-yoda-and-the-hover-pram/1100-6528183/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6528183\"\u003eStar Wars\u003c/a\u003e, and more popular franchises.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eNew Lego Harry Potter Sets\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building/dp/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLego Harry Potter - Diagon Alley (2,750 pieces)\u003c/a\u003e -- $200\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Harry-Potter-Malfoy-Building/dp/B0DHLGSV88?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLego Harry Potter - Malfoy Manor (1,601 pieces)\u003c/a\u003e -- $150\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Harry-Potter-Burrow-Collectible/dp/B0DF83ZF1G?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLego Harry Potter - The Burrow Collector\u0026#39;s Edition (2,405 pieces)\u003c/a\u003e -- $260\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Harry-Potter-Hogwarts-Castle/dp/B0DJ1B25K9?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLego Harry Potter - Hogwarts Castle: Flying Lessons (651 pieces)\u003c/a\u003e -- $80\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Potter-Hagrid-Motorcycle-Building/dp/B0DJ18XKWX?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLego Harry Potter - Hagrid \u0026amp; Harry’s Motorcycle Ride (617 pieces)\u003c/a\u003e -- $50\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Harry-Potter-Hogwarts-Castle/dp/B0DJ18LDHN?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLego Harry Potter - Hogwarts Castle: Dueling Club (158 pieces)\u003c/a\u003e -- $25\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Harry-Potter-Hogwarts-Castle/dp/B0DJ1BV2TX?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLego Harry Potter - Hogwarts Castle: Charms Class (204 pieces)\u003c/a\u003e -- $20\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cdiv title=\"6528569 - New Lego Harry Potter Sets 2025\" data-embed-type=\"buylink\" data-ref-id=\"3015\" data-template=\"4\" data-size=\"buylink__listicle\" data-title=\"6528569 - New Lego Harry Potter Sets 2025\" data-collection=\"\"\u003e                                                                     \u003cdiv\u003e             \u003ch2\u003e                    \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building/dp/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{\u0026#34;destUrl\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building\\/dp\\/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;dwLinkTag\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;leadType\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;deal\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;linkLocation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;BuyButton\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;seamlessScrollPage\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;searchDim\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;}\" data-track-page-event=\"{\u0026#34;eventName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Monetization Link Clicked\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantPrice\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building/dp/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\"\u003eLego Harry Potter - Diagon Alley (2,750 Pieces)\u003c/a\u003e       \u003c/h2\u003e                                   \u003ch3\u003e                      \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building/dp/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{\u0026#34;destUrl\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building\\/dp\\/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;dwLinkTag\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;leadType\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;deal\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;linkLocation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;BuyButton\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;seamlessScrollPage\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;searchDim\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;}\" data-track-page-event=\"{\u0026#34;eventName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Monetization Link Clicked\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantPrice\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building/dp/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\"\u003e$200\u003c/a\u003e         \u003c/h3\u003e                                                                                                        \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_medium/1595/15950357/4421257-diagonalley.jpg\"/\u003e                             \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building/dp/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{\u0026#34;destUrl\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building\\/dp\\/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;dwLinkTag\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;leadType\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;deal\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;linkLocation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;BuyButton\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;seamlessScrollPage\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;1\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;searchDim\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;}\" data-track-page-event=\"{\u0026#34;eventName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Monetization Link Clicked\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;merchantPrice\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-buy-link=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Potter-Diagon-Wizarding-Building/dp/B0DHLHLX1B?tag=gamespot-promos-20\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e                        \u003c/p\u003e              \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eArguably one of the coolest Harry Potter building sets Lego has released thus far, the expansive and richly detailed recreation of Diagon Alley looks to be quite the treat for big fans of the franchise. The 2,750-piece build can be displayed as a two-sided street (shown above), one row of buildings with Gringotts as the centerpiece, or as five distinct modules.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHarry Potter fans will build many of the best-known shops and businesses found in the books and movies: Gringotts Wizarding Bank, Ollivanders Wand Shop, The Daily Prophet HQ, The Leaky Cauldron, Weasleys\u0026#39; Wizard Wheezes, Florean Fortescue\u0026#39;s Ice Cream Parlor, and Mr. Mulpepper\u0026#39;s Apothecary. Along with authentic exterior designs, the buildings in Diagon Alley have plenty of Easter Eggs for fans to discover while building.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDiagon Alley without witches and wizards would be a sad place, so thankfully this set also comes with 12 Harry Potter Lego microfigures, including:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eHarry Potter\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eHermione Granger\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eRon Weasley\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eFred Weasley\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eGeorge Weasley\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eGinny Weasley\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eLavender Brown\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eDraco Malfoy\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eNarcissa Malfoy\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMr. Borgin\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Diagon Alley set also comes with the Knight Bus and various accessories for the walkways outside of the shops.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis isn\u0026#39;t the first time Lego has released a Diagon Alley build. A \u003ca href=\"https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fclick.linksynergy.com%2Fdeeplink%3Fid%3DVZfI20jEa0c%26mid%3D13923%26u1%3Dsubid_value%26murl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.lego.com%2Fen-us%2Fproduct%2Fdiagon-alley-75978\u0026amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fnew-2750-piece-lego-harry-potter-set-recreates-diagon-alley%2F1100-6528569%2F%3Fftag%3DGSS-05-10aac1i\u0026amp;event_type=click\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003e5,544-piece Diagon Alley set\u003c/a\u003e launched as a Lego Store exclusive back in 2020. It remains an exclusive to this day and is actually still available, but it costs $450. The old version has bigger shops but fewer overall buildings. So the new $200 model gives fans a more budget-friendly way to build the famous Wizarding World shopping plaza.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e                      \u003c/div\u003e                                                                     \u003cdiv\u003e             \u003ch2\u003e                    \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/LEGO-Harry-Potter-Malfoy-Building/dp/B0DHLGSV88?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-event-tracking=\"{\u0026#34;destUrl\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/LEGO-Harry-Potter-Malfoy-Building\\/dp\\/B0DHLGSV88?tag=gamespot-promos-20\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;dwLinkTag\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;listicle|button\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;leadType\u0026#34;:\u